title: Victorinox eLLa - discover your city & join the eLLawalk
description: The new Victorinox eLLa perfume arouses your wanderlust: Create your eLLawalk, a personal discovery tour, made of different spots. Simply photo-graph your favourite places with your Instagram app and create your personal eLLawalk on your desktop computer.

asset.author: Victorinox AG
asset.hookText:
The new Victorinox eLLa perfume arouses your wanderlust: Create your eLLawalk, a personal discovery tour, made of different spots. Simply photo-graph your favourite places with your Instagram app and create your personal eLLawalk on your desktop computer. This will not only gather your favourite spots, but also allow others to be inspired by your eLLawalk. 
EMBRACE THE WORLD - BE PART OF THE FIRST GLOBAL TRAVEL GUIDE FOR AND FROM WOMEN!
www.ellawalk.com
